note: Cefali & Cefali are personal injury attorneys located in Orange County, California, specifically in the city of San Juan Capistrano. The firm handles every kind of personal injury case including car accidents, trucking accidents, bicycle accidents, motorcycle accidents, boating accidents, pedestrian accidents, rideshare accidents, slip and fall cases, whiplash injuries, dog bite injuries, accidents involving brain injuries, assault and battery injuries, and accidents involving DUI or DWI.
